Design High Availability for:

• API Server
• etcd
• Scheduler

Solution:-

1️⃣ API Server

• Multiple replicas
• Behind Load Balancer
• Stateless → easy scaling

2️⃣ etcd

• Odd number cluster (3, 5, 7)
• Uses quorum (majority voting)
• Spread across AZs
• Regular backups

3️⃣ Scheduler

• Multiple instances
• Leader election
• One active, others standby

4️⃣ Controller Manager (Important Add)

• Also uses leader election

# Rule of Thumb
Type	Strategy
Stateless	Replicate
Stateful (etcd)	Quorum
Leader-based	Leader Election
